                        <img src="img/shopping-cart.png" width="26px" alt="" class="shopping-cart">
                        <span class="carrito rose">0</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <section class="cuerpo">
        <section class="slider">
            <main>
                <div class="content">
                    <!-- Pieces Slider -->
                    <div class="pieces-slider">
                        <!-- Each slide with corresponding image and text -->
                        <div class="pieces-slider__slide">
                            <img class="pieces-slider__image" src="img/galery/1-0.jpg" alt="">
                            <h2 class="pieces-slider__text">Love Letters</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pieces-slider__slide">
                            <img class="pieces-slider__image" src="img/galery/1-5.jpg" alt="">
                            <h2 class="pieces-slider__text">Love Letters</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pieces-slider__slide">
                            <img class="pieces-slider__image" src="img/galery/1-2.jpg" alt="">
                            <h2 class="pieces-slider__text">Love Letters</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pieces-slider__slide">
                            <img class="pieces-slider__image" src="img/galery/1-4.jpg" alt="">
                            <h2 class="pieces-slider__text">Love Letters</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pieces-slider__slide">
                            <img class="pieces-slider__image" src="img/galery/1-1.jpg" alt="">
                            <h2 class="pieces-slider__text">Love Letters</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pieces-slider__slide">
                            <img class="pieces-slider__image" src="img/galery/1-3.jpg" alt="">
                            <h2 class="pieces-slider__text">Love Letters</h2>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Canvas to draw the pieces -->
                        <canvas class="pieces-slider__canvas"></canvas>
                        <!-- Slider buttons: prev and next -->
                        <button class="pieces-slider__button pieces-slider__button--prev bb-custom-icon bb-custom-icon-arrow-left"></button>
                        <button class="pieces-slider__button pieces-slider__button--next bb-custom-icon bb-custom-icon-arrow-right"></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </section>
        <section class="otracosa">
            <div class="cont-desc-aut">
                <div class="cont-dos-desc-aut">
                    <h1 class="til">Melanie Cockcroft</h1>
                    <p>Melanie Cockcroft Diaz was born the 20th of September 1996 in Cali, Colombia but has a British nationality.
                        Ever since she was little, she had a passion for traveling and discovering new things about the world
                        around her. At first, she did not enjoy reading and writing since she preferred to gain experience
                        first-hand, however, as many years went by she came to love it. She has entered in school writing
                        competitions and has had positive criticism on the depth and diversity of her writing styles despite
                        having dyslexia. Her fluency in English and Spanish, along with her knowledge of other languages
                        and cultures, give her characters a complex thought pattern that seems straight at first glance.
                        As the first book she has ever published, she was unable to contract a professional model for the
                        book and decided to portrait herself instead.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="cont-img-aut">
                <img src="img\thumbs\author.png" width="226" class="img" />
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="interaction">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="cont-comen">
                    <div class="comentario">
                        <p class="desc-comen">Escribe tu nombre y una corta historia. podrás publicarla para que aparezcan al interior del libro
                            y así otras personas la leerán.</p>
                        <input type="text" id="myName" placeholder="Nombre">
                        <textarea id="comen" class="comen" name="comentario" rows="5" cols="50" placeholder="Escribe tu Historia: "></textarea>
                        <div class="cont-button-subir">
                            <button type="submit" id="subir" class="subir" onclick="enviarDatos()">Continue</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bb-custom-wrapper">
                    <div id="bb-bookblock" class="bb-bookblock">
                        <div class="bb-item">
                            <div class="bb-custom-firstpage">

                            </div>
                            <div class="bb-custom-side">
                                <img src="img/1-21.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        {{#each result1}}
                        <div class="bb-item">
                            <div class="bb-custom-side">
                                <img class="fondoLib" src="img/galery/1-15.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="bb-custom-side">
                                <h1>{{nombre}}</h1>
                                <p>{{mensaje}}</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        {{/each}}
                    </div>

                    <nav>
                        <a id="bb-nav-first" href="#" class="bb-custom-icon bb-custom-icon-first">First page</a>
                        <a id="bb-nav-prev" href="#" class="bb-custom-icon bb-custom-icon-arrow-left">Previous</a>
                        <a id="bb-nav-next" href="#" class="bb-custom-icon bb-custom-icon-arrow-right">Next</a>
                        <a id="bb-nav-last" href="#" class="bb-custom-icon bb-custom-icon-last">Last page</a>
                    </nav>

                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="regis">
            <div class="text">
                <div class="titulo">
                    <h1>Let's stay in touch.</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="sub">
                    <h2>Register to be the first to know the news.</h2>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="correo">
                <input type="email" name="" id="cuadro" placeholder="Give us your mail (’O’ )">
                <button class="bot-submit hvr-bounce-to-right" id="botSubmit">Submit</button>
            </div>

        </section>
    </section>
    <div id='main-cont1'>
        <a href='#' id='container1' class='container'>
